descript.purpose:
*** Last Updated November 2010 *** An updated Trails network for Mercer County, New Jersey. Trails include existing as well as propsed, planned and conceptual trails located through out the county.
General information includes type of trail (Park Path, Greenway, Loop, Network Connector. long distance corridor), material of trail as well as contact information, hours and end points (where available).
